==Finnish== 
===Verb===

Nussia ''(vulgar)''

# ''(With the object in the partitive case)'' To fuck, screw, have sex. ''Sinähän et nussi mun siskoani!'' You will not fuck my sister!
# ''(With the object in the genitive-accusative case)'' To steal, snatch, [[feck]]. ''Kuka vittu on nussinut mun lompakkoni?'' Who the fuck has snatched my wallet?

Finnish synonyms: [[panna]], [[hässiä]], [[naida]]
